    "titles": {
      "en": "Divine sustenance and accountability parallels"
    },
    "verse_count": 4,
    "verse_start_index": 1868,
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ],
    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 1869,
        "local_index": 1,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:190:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/300/367",
        "text": [
          "٣٠٠. وَسُئِلَ (عليه السلام) : كَيْفَ يُحَاسِبُ اللَّهُ الْخَلْقَ عَلَى كَثْرَتِهِمْ؟"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "300. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, was asked: How Allāh would conduct the accounting of all persons despite their large number."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1870,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:190:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/300/368",
        "text": [
          "فَقَالَ (عليه السلام) : كَمَا يَرْزُقُهُمْ عَلَى كَثْرَتِهِمْ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "He replied: Just as He provides them livelihood despite their large number."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1871,
        "local_index": 3,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:190:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/300/369",
        "text": [
          "فَقِيلَ: كَيْفَ يُحَاسِبُهُمْ وَلَا يَرَوْنَهُ؟"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "Then it was said to him: How will He conduct their accounting without their seeing Him."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1872,
        "local_index": 4,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:190:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/300/370",
        "text": [
          "فَقَالَ (عليه السلام) : كَمَا يَرْزُقُهُمْ وَلَا يَرَوْنَهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "He replied: Just as He provides them livelihood although they do not see Him."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
